title: Mordor Invasion of Dol Guldur: Elves and Dwarves Stand United - Third Age Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
Mordor has sent a full scale invasion to take Dol Guldur.  But the Elves and Dwarves stand united to protect the forest of Mirkwood.  This will be an epic siege battle show down!  Enjoy the Battle :D

Third Age Reforged is a submod for Third Age Total War. 


If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
